Package us.ullberg.startpunkt.crd.v1alpha4

Class ApplicationSpec

java.lang.Object
us.ullberg.startpunkt.crd.v1alpha4.ApplicationSpec
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<ApplicationSpec>
Direct Known Subclasses:
ApplicationSpecWithAvailability
public class ApplicationSpec extends Object implements Comparable<ApplicationSpec>
Represents a single application bookmark specification in the Startpunkt UI.

This object defines all metadata related to a user-facing bookmark or link, such as its name, group, URL, icon, sorting order, visibility, and display behavior. It is typically used as the spec section in a Kubernetes custom resource representing application shortcuts.

The name and url fields are required. Other fields are optional and enhance the UI experience.
